is a serious matter.

1062
01:02:26,121 --> 01:02:28,498
Not to mention abduction.

1063
01:02:28,582 --> 01:02:30,333
- Abduction?
- Yeah.

1064
01:02:30,417 --> 01:02:32,210
Off the record.

1065
01:02:32,294 --> 01:02:34,045
