1075
01:03:01,865 --> 01:03:03,492
All right.

1076
01:03:03,575 --> 01:03:05,160
You've got a deal.

1077
01:03:06,703 --> 01:03:09,247
You want to see her?
You're gonna see her!

1078
01:03:10,916 --> 01:03:12,375
Good!

