an awful lot of smoke.

1088
01:03:38,443 --> 01:03:40,654
Well, that's the way
she wants it.

1089
01:03:40,695 --> 01:03:42,864
After you told us
about the death threats,

1090
01:03:42,906 --> 01:03:45,200
