off the crowd.

1092
01:03:46,952 --> 01:03:49,871
Excellent. Here, Simone wanted
you to have these.

1093
01:03:49,955 --> 01:03:51,456
- Unreal.
- And remember--

1094
01:03:51,540 --> 01:03:53,417
