that you can't stop
talking about Viktor?

1161
01:08:42,205 --> 01:08:43,665
I have to talk to her.

1162
01:08:47,753 --> 01:08:49,671
I've been meaning
to talk to you.

1163
01:08:51,047 --> 01:08:54,426
