Goodwill Tour of the third world.

1237
01:12:59,546 --> 01:13:01,465
Ladies and gentlemen,
Simone!

1238
01:13:06,052 --> 01:13:07,804
Thank you.
Oh, thank you.

1239
01:13:07,888 --> 01:13:10,265
This means
so much to me.

1240
01:13:10,307 --> 01:13:13,143
I'm just sorry I couldn't
be there with you.

